{"tid":1508024,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[9月方向] 和理非行動全面升級","createTime":"2019-08-26T11:34:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T17:15:46.000Z","uid":104507,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"c55293f7960c97a06547ea054dfd0d12f50ec208","tid":1508024,"uid":104507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T11:34:08.000Z","msg":"自7月中開始，勇武行得實在太快喇，<br />\n和理非係時候急起直追！<br />\n追撚住政府春袋嚟打！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n建議9月開始嘅星期六同日，<br />\n各自定一日<span style=\"color: orange;\">機埸</span>及一日<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">商埸</span>。<br />\n唔代表勇武同地區抗爭要暫停喎，<br />\n而係要將佢變成<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>突擊戰</strong></span>，唔須要比任何預告。<br />\n就唔會比到時間狗狗部署，亦唔會比到黨鐵封站<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E5DXAnL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE5DXAnL.jpg&h=e001229c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n打破平行時空，將抗爭帶入商埸。<br />\n以<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">商場</span>為總部，方便出發，遊擊，突襲，逃走。<br />\n和理非繼續係商埸shopping，對準自由行輸出革命，勇武到時去邊任你玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n兩邊同時進行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3i2mcne.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3i2mcne.png&h=23da3521&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">機埸</span>唔洗多講，最近好多巴絲都出咗post。陳帆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有一眾航空業界巴絲，佢地好需要我地嘅鼎力支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">機埸=<strong>政府春袋</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">各大高級商埸=<strong>地產商商家佬春袋</strong></span></span><br />\n對準政權，玩到封商埸、出禁制令，間接支持罷買日，打擊埋自由行。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">當中加插返地區遊行，務求次次新鮮獲獲甘。<br />\n最緊要玩到十月一號，一同慶祝中共70週歲。</strong><br />\n</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">相關討論：<br />\n林鄭提哂水：《No stake in the society》商場大作戰要開始了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1439464\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1439464</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我地係前線空管主任，我地跪求大家一定要支持航空業既巴打絲打<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1498685\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1498685</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />\n<br />\n以下開放討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可。<br />\n和勇一家，團結抗暴。<br />\n我要</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">真普選</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/gold][/b]"},{"pid":"dedcbce5dbf5bb7e697d264ab69264b25fdc9feb","tid":1508024,"uid":35842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T11:34:25.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣傳一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wjFi3Tp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwjFi3Tp.jpg&h=1a5d1359&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">901 和你塞 13:00 見</span></span> <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsZzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=df402bec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\n現有文宣集合 (Google Drive)<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsZzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=7411ddd8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2</a><br />\n請隨便使用，用自己的方法幫忙發送文宣出去，感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LoOsXdt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLoOsXdt.jpg&h=b1104862&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">每晚10點</span></strong></span>大家開大嗰窗嗌口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當係抒發下或者互相鼓勵都好<br />\n<br />\n真係有人嗌㗎 唔洗怕醜<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/fit.tsoi/videos/189596038709864/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffit.tsoi%2Fvideos%2F189596038709864%2F&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsZzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=8b392e0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/fit.tsoi/videos/189596038709864/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1170684516349159/posts/2398098013607797?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1170684516349159%2Fposts%2F2398098013607797%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsZzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=4f3e919a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1170684516349159/posts/2398098013607797?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/102458676557543/posts/1582783125191750?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F102458676557543%2Fposts%2F1582783125191750%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsZzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=6f9ef42f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/102458676557543/posts/1582783125191750?sfns=mo</a><br />\n將窗嗌口號變成一種普及的生活方式，會好大感染力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b0424ebffa0dfdad2e8f25af3cff70765bc6685","tid":1508024,"uid":28159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T11:36:05.000Z","msg":"港鐵商場好似德福嗰啲咁好生意 多咗人都唔覺啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb0387ad0d598c3552f98a803876426416917f45","tid":1508024,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T11:36:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4B5ZOzj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4B5ZOzj.gif&h=0e4bb77e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsZzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=df402bec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsZzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=b6407e40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou